{"tid":2451444,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"西區區議會： 政府不批准區議會討論封區 指封區不是地區層面事宜","createTime":"2021-03-18T06:02:20.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-19T02:14:09.000Z","uid":22556,"like":2,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"a0b1d4d82b0587e6c6c24457b127e0a6158f7b12","tid":2451444,"uid":22556,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-18T06:02:20.000Z","msg":"【火滾！震驚中西區24萬居民！】<br />\n<br />\n剛搞完封區，剛到 區原定1點開會，政府竟然唔比區議會一陣討論以下兩項：<br />\n1） 大廈強制檢測的混亂安排<br />\n2）封區及解封的混亂安排<br />\n<br />\n政府DQ了我們的討論項目，而佢個解釋係：<br />\n<br />\n／／由於上述文件涉及的議題並非中西區地區層面的事宜，政府認為上述文件的討論內容並不符合《區議會條例》第61條所述有關區議會的職能。／／<br />\n<br />\n過去一星期，近百座大廈強制檢測，加上封了4日區，咁都唔關中西區的地區事務事？ 講得通嗎？真係救命呀<br />\n────────<br />\n<br />\n我地都只係想討論一下這些街坊的具體意見：<br />\n<br />\n【檢測的人流分流問題？】<br />\n－ 例如分流叫不同樓層住戶去下面做檢測，例如幾至幾樓，避免多人聚集，增加感染機會，同大排長龍。<br />\n<br />\n【排隊的指引及公平性問題？】<br />\n－老人家及其他人士可優先排隊？現指示不足<br />\n<br />\n【行動不便者如何何處理？】<br />\n－個別體弱人士或有少少病徵人士應安排在家個別上門檢測安排，是否可加人手上門為長者做檢測？<br />\n<br />\n【食宵夜咩？】<br />\n－食物原來非即食仲要check 完先有.已經十二點，有乜用？其實上門登記就已經可派<br />\n<br />\n 【檢測前不可飲食？】<br />\n－沒有指引<br />\n<br />\n【6歲以下是否須檢測？ 】<br />\n－眾說紛紜，有一說是可拎樽，另一說是不用檢測。究竟是需要還是不需要？<br />\n<br />\n【商戶幾時可開舖？】<br />\n－政府無人清楚講到<br />\n<br />\n【茶樓茶客需要檢測？】<br />\n－政府無人清楚講到<br />\n<br />\n議會直播中，齊齊見證政府荒謬：<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/cwdclive/videos/775440703087143/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fcwdclive%2Fvideos%2F775440703087143%2F&d=1mBOIAkAA7%2FwaZBThmus2QfwWQc8qO99IFO6%2BGFOovI%3D&h=82800341\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/cwdclive/videos/775440703087143/</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/113061346712567/posts/477599006925464/?d=n\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F113061346712567%2Fposts%2F477599006925464%2F%3Fd%3Dn&d=1mBOIAkAA7%2FwaZBThmus2QfwWQc8qO99IFO6%2BGFOovI%3D&h=1b46a0e9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/113061346712567/posts/477599006925464/?d=n</a>"},{"pid":"bb0c28a27dab36c1519dfe249895843955ab3022","tid":2451444,"uid":22556,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-18T06:02:42.000Z","msg":"中西區區議會先岩🤦🏼&zwj;♂️"},{"pid":"6fa6a021034463e7d5d4e2a2e4653e216c5b597d","tid":2451444,"uid":48362,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-18T06:03:57.000Z","msg":"將來強姦都唔係性罪行 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a443b601ea5f085ca0f136ad7bd7d54125e6e8b8","tid":2451444,"uid":63154,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-18T06:05:54.000Z","msg":"吓？人哋只係討論個過程可以點照顧居民，係討論點做好啲，咁都唔得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"78f9d6f6d1fbb191f2c6bb4e8ffdfafbd576a29d","tid":2451444,"uid":254450,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-18T06:06:00.000Z","msg":"總之區議會傾乜都唔得，講香港嘢就係將d嘢政治化，搞港獨，謀求推返国家政權<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d620f5a0dc24eca55132454770ebaed520293636","tid":2451444,"uid":177578,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-18T06:08:15.000Z","msg":"係時候討論<br />\n中美冷戰期間<br />\n區議會既定位<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a2508ef287f399216b3cda137e38795a5b1ec855","tid":2451444,"uid":38757,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-18T06:09:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />咁都唔係地區層面既事?"},{"pid":"3807613e8e4778580c7d7379864d52127ed6b310","tid":2451444,"uid":45684,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"cit